Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,‎谁是美人呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Who's a pretty girl, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎谁是美人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Who's a pretty girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就是你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你看什么呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他告诉我们把财物藏在这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He told us to place possessions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎以便日后需要的时候好找\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to aid later identification if need be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我要看看是否管用\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I needed to see if it still worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我要去见艾萨克\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm going to see Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不会带它去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm not taking it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我可以问你个问题吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}May I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎当然可以\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们在这里干什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这问题太宽泛了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That is a very broad question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎说得具体点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎坐下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不必向你解释\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I do not need to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎黑暗生物是什么样的 锻造师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}what night creatures are, forgemaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎叫我艾萨克就行\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You can call me Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你要吃个浆果吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Would you like a berry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这就是个例子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Case in point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am a night creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我吃肉喝血\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I eat blood and meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,‎吃个浆果也许不会要你的命\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A berry would probably not kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎黑暗生物杀戮\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Night creatures kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎毁灭和掠夺\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}destroy and despoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是我们的荣幸\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It is our pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎黑暗生物要服从锻造师的意志\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Night creatures do the will of their forgemasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那么也许 ‎我根本不了解你的意志\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Then perhaps I simply don't understand your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你让我们把人埋起来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You have us burying people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这座城里遍地都是死人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The city was littered with dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎太多人腐烂得厉害\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Too many of them were too decayed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,无法用魔法转化\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to be converted by magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以要埋葬他们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So they need to be buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你不是傻瓜\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You are not a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎会有昆虫和疾病滋生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Insects and diseases would breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我提醒你 这里所有人都是受害者\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I would remind you that everyone here was a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们应该被安葬\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They deserve a burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那为什么我们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Then why do we care
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎要操心昆虫和疾病呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}about insects and diseases?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎想问就问吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Ask your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们杀戮 毁灭和掠夺\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We kill, destroy and despoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你却让我们埋葬腐烂的死人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You have us burying the rotten dead
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎重建和修复这个地方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and rebuilding and repairing this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你为什么要让我们违背自己的本性\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why do you have us going against our nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你们的本性易变\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Your nature is fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你相信自己是毁灭的工具\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You believe you are tools of destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎只因为你的同胞一直被这样利用\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}only because this is how your kind have always been used.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎吃个浆果吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Have a berry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎回忆起来了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这不是血 也不是肉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's not blood or meat,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但你吃了似乎也没有丧命\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but you don't appear to have died from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我来回答你的问题\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'll answer your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这个城市曾经居住着成千上百人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This city was once home to many hundreds of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许还有更多人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}perhaps more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎等到尸体被掩埋\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It could be resettled,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎废墟被处理 建筑被修复\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}once the bodies are buried,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎人们就可以重新在此定居\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}the debris is disposed of and the structures are repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们很快就要走了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We will be moving on soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎等我们走了之后\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}After we are gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这座城市将留下来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}the city will be here for people to find
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎人们会找到这里安家\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and make homes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你想再吃个浆果吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Would you like another berry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,‎吃一个吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你看 你可以用锤子盖房子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You see, you can use a hammer to build a house
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也可以敲碎头骨\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}or crack a skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你作为工具重返人间\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You are returned to earth as tools,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我会按我的想法使用工具\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and I will use tools as I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎有好多回忆\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So many memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我最终也可以选择\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can also choose, in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎承认你根本不是工具\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to recognize that you are not tools at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为没有工具尝到浆果\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}For no tool would taste a berry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还会记得前世\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and remember the time in its first life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,吃到浆果的时光\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}when it encountered them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我们是来自地狱的生物...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But we are creatures of hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎奉命去战斗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to be commanded to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎总有一天 地狱会空荡荡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}One day, hell will be emptied
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎地狱之门会在风中作响\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and its doors will rattle in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎借着我的手\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Through my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎上帝以他的怜悯 ‎从地狱中解救被诅咒的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}God lifts the damned from hell in his mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎成为我的士兵 在人间赎罪\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to enact their penance on the Earth as my soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-‎是的  -‎他们在人间的赎罪\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- Yes. - Should their penance on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也应该永恒不变吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}be eternal too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不清楚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我也不清楚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们应该一起弄清楚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We should find out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎在此期间\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}In the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们可以做的事情\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}we can both do a little more
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎比我们想要做的多一些\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}than what we were intended for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我能说句话吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}May I make an observation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎说吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You may.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你变了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You are changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我觉得你还想复仇\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There is still revenge in you, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但也有其他想法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But other things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们还要战斗吗 艾萨克\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are we still fighting, Isaac?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们总是有战斗的理由\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're always fighting for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我明白你的意思\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But I take your meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎快了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他也许说得有道理\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He might have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你觉得呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我花了几周时间\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It took me a few weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎转化这座城市中能用的尸体\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to transform the viable bodies in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎又花了几周时间完成修复 并埋葬那些\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Weeks more to effect repairs and bury those
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,损坏得无法转化的尸体\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}too destroyed to convert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我抽出时间想一想\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Is it so bad to take my time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这有什么不好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and think for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是我变了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Have I changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎说吧 说点什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Go on, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我杀了你 老巫师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I killed you, old wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你肯定对这事有意见\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You must have an opinion on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没有吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我杀过很多人 老巫师 原因有很多\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have killed many people, old wizard, for many reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但杀你只是凭感觉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But killing you felt just.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎感觉像是一点点修复这个世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It felt like repairing the world a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我喜欢那种感觉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I liked that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很长一段时间\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}For a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我满足于做别人手里的刀\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was content to be the knife that others wielded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不过最近 ‎老巫师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But lately, old wizard,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我觉得自己更像是手 而不是刀\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have felt more like the hand than the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我这辈子都被动应对\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}My whole life, I have reacted to things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很少主动出击\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Rarely acted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以 ‎是的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我变了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我能控制这个世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have agency in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我能创造未来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can create futures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎幸好 我可以创造未来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And, happily, I could create a future
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎同时终结你们的未来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and end yours at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎上帝是仁慈的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}God is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不知道接下来会做什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I wonder what I will do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎镜子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎镜子先生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sir Mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你要做什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你是哪位\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你不记得我了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you not remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你看起来不容易被人记住\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You do not look memorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎瓦尼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Varney.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎德古拉伯爵原来的手下瓦尼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Varney of Dracula's original cohort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在战争初期去了塔哥维斯特\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I left for Targoviste early in the campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你为什么要连接到我的镜子 瓦尼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why are you connecting to my mirror, Varney?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那个标出你在各地行踪的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have spoken with people who marked your passage
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎跟我谈过了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}across the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你做得很不错 先生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You have done great work, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你还没回答我的问题\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}My question is pending.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎锻造师艾萨克\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am working to bring about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在努力让德古拉起死回生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Dracula's return from the dead, Isaac Forgemaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真有意思\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}How very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不止如此\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我一直在和各地的魔法师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've been speaking with magicians and scholars
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎和学者们交谈\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}across the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎有吸血鬼 也有人类\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Both vampire and human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一起努力搜集古老的魔咒和知识\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Working together to collect ancient spells and lore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎设计出一套方法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Constructing a system
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎从地狱中救出德古拉伯爵\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}with which to pluck Dracula from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎让他重掌天下大权\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and reinstall him in the world with power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那又会怎样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}To what end?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他还有未尽的事业 先生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He has unfinished business, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他欠我们的是死亡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He owes us death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎数量空前的死亡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Death in volumes unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他的伟大事业还没有完成\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}His great work remains incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我也有未尽的事业 瓦尼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So does mine, Varney.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你的事业难道像\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, is yours as important
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎灭绝杀死他妻子的种族一样重要吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}as the extinction of the race that killed his wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你自己都讨厌的种族\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The race that you yourself hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,‎对我来说很重要\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It is to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们拭目以待吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Afterwards, we will see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我对德古拉最喜爱的锻造师期望过高了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I expected better than that of Dracula's favored forgemaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎等到太阳升起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Then, come daylight,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你就会在你的棺材里失望地打滚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}you can wriggle in your little coffin with disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但是不要吵闹 ‎因为我完成自己的使命前\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But do it quietly, as I do not wish to hear your voice again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不想再听到你的声音\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}until my own task is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎镜子先生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sir Mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别再让这个人召唤我了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}do not allow this one to call me again,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎去睡吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎去你的…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Fuck you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他不听我说完\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Ugh! He cut me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我觉得你让他烦透了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think you bored him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他不知道我是谁吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Doesn't he know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,‎哦 拜托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是瓦尼 伦敦的瓦尼 ‎从伦敦建成以来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm Varney. Varney of London. Since before it was London.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎伦敦还是罗马鬼城时 我就很强大\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was mighty when London was a Roman ghost town
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们还用人头骨来标记我们的边界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and we still marked our borders out with human skulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他去死吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Fuck him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没有他 我们自己干\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We'll do it without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我改变主意了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎让士兵用床抬着我在乡间游走\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Have soldiers carry me around the countryside on a bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在开玩笑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was making a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不在乎 去做吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't care. Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎浑身都疼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Everything hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吧 也没那么糟\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, this isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们在这里待了几周了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We've been out here for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不想知道还能有多糟\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't want to know how it can get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎-那么…  ‎-我说过 我不想知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- Well, it... - I said I don't want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不想再听你讲什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't want to hear any more of your stories
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎马鞍疮和吃老鼠的故事了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}about saddle boils and eating rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吧 但我跟你说过 ‎我看到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All right, all right, but did I tell you about the time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,18只松鼠杀一条狗的故事吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I saw 18 squirrels murder a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看在上帝的份上 闭嘴吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}In the name of God, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎给你 喝了就不疼了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Here. Dull the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这样不对\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我爱你 但说真的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I love you, but, really,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我准备送你坐上马车回家\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm ready to put you on a wagon home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这种情形\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们到处奔走...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We've been touring...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还没走完卡米拉标记的领土\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not even the entire territory Camilla marked out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎只完成了一小部分\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}just a piece of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...都几周了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}...for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这样不对\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And this is all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎女人 解释一下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Explain yourself, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不是特别喜欢人类\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have no particular love for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们位于食物链的顶端\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's a food chain, and we're on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎人类不过是穿鞋的猪\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Humans are pigs with shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们想吃培根的时候 不会掉眼泪\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and they don't cry when they want bacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我把人类变成食物 也不会难过\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am not sad when I turn humans into food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎明白吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎有话直说 莫拉娜\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Spit it out, Morana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎有什么想法直接说出来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Directly say what you're thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不然你会感到困扰\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}or you'll tie yourself up in knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎天啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你在一起生活太久了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have lived with you for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吧 有没有迅速而仁慈的方法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Okay, is there a swift and merciful way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎让我们控制从城堡到大海之间\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}for us to take control of all the designated territory
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所有划定的领土\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}between the castle and the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你是说 打个响指就搞定吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You mean, snap my fingers and it's all done?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不 当然没有\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎当然没有\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这会是逐步推进的硬仗 对吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It will be hard-fought, mile by mile, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吧 别说得那么露骨\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, let's not make it sound desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但这绝不简单\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But it won't be simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也会有苦难\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There will be suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是战争 莫拉娜 总是会有苦难\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's war, Morana. There's always suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这不是战争\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's not war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没有对战的双方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There are no two sides to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是步步紧逼的进攻\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's a rolling invasion
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎对几十万人的诱捕\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and entrapment of hundreds of thousands of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不幸的是 人类比猪聪明\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Humans who are, sadly, cleverer than pigs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们会战斗 痛苦 恐惧和逃跑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and will fight and suffer and fear and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那我换个说法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Then I choose a different word.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是"战役"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's "battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我跟你来到这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I came out here with you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我想亲眼看看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}because I wanted to see for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这个计划有什么后勤困难\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}the logistical challenges to the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我跟你说了 你不用非得来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I told you, you didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我会视察战场\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'd survey the theater of combat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你我需要什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and let you know what I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还有...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你问过我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}you're the one who asked me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是否想指挥一个帝国\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}if I wanted to command an empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的 我知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎在家里就更能理解了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It made a lot more sense back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎专心点 莫拉娜\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Focus, Morana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎别因为我不是军人就教训我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Don't talk down to me because I am not a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这将是可怕的烂摊子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is going to be a horrifying mess
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们有生之年都要收拾这个烂摊子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}that we will be dealing with till the end of our days,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这场战争将造成 ‎历史上前所未有的苦难\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and it will cause more suffering than history has yet seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎别因为我是军人就对我摆架子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Don't condescend to me because I am a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我能打赢战争\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I win wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎过了这么长时间 你突然质疑我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are you suddenly doubting me after all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是否因为你过我的生活累得腿疼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}because your legs are sore from living my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你准备在下半辈子‎一次又一次\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are you ready to fight the same war over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,打同样的战争吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}for the rest of your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你想知道我的想法吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You want to know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎洗耳恭听\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想 无论取得什么成就\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think that whatever we achieve,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们都要一起实现\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}we achieve it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就你和我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎卡米拉抛出疯狂的计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla throws a crazy plan at us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们来推行这个计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and it's us who make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎换句话说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Or, put another way,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎尽管有卡米拉 还是我们来实施计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}we make it work despite Carmilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎丽诺尔从来都帮不上忙\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And Lenore's never any bloody help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她大部分时间都有点怪\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She's off with the fairies most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎只有我们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在家的时候‎更能理解这个疯狂的计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And the crazy plan makes sense back home because,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我也不清楚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为卡米拉有扭曲现实的魔法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla has this magic reality distortion spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们为自己能实施计划感到骄傲\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and we pride ourselves on making things work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我们在这里待了几周 ‎\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But we've been out here for weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎远离卡米拉和她的疯狂 我要跟你说…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}away from her and her madness, and I'm telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎怎么回事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎有人偷袭\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎黎明时分\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}At dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们知道我们的身份\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They know what we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,‎显然他们不傻\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And apparently they're not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用我的箱子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I need to get to my trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那个箱子吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你从来没打开过\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You never open that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,里面是什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎白昼盔甲\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Day armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎躲进箱子里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Get in the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎箭射不进去 光也照不进去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Arrows can't pierce it and light can't get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎躲进该死的箱子里 亲爱的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Get in the damn trunk, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎快点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎烧死他们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Burn them alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎来吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎叫他们出来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Bring them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎过来吧 狗杂种\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Over here, dogfuckers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这就对了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎该死的傻畜生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Idiot fucking livestock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,施第里尔的士兵\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Soldiers of Styria!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎穿上盔甲遮住皮肤\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Armor up and cover your skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我们赢了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I take it we won.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很好 我想亲手杀了你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Good. I want to kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你知道这个箱子有多难闻吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you know what this thing smells like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们不是战士\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They weren't fighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们只是普通人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They were just people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎村民\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎农民什么的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Farmers and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不想反驳你对卡米拉的看法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't disagree with what you said about Carmilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:20:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她是我的好朋友\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She's my dear friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我们都知道她是什么人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but we both know what she's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我的确不同意打这场仗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I did disagree about the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎只要我投入战斗 ‎就没有我打不赢的战役\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's no battle I can't win when I put my back into it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我身边有你和你的头脑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and I have you and your mind beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚击退了该死的农民\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I just fought fucking farmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看到他们眼中的恐惧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Saw the fear in their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不是害怕去死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not fear of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而是害怕没有打过仗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Fear of not having fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎害怕救不了他们的族人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Fear of not saving their people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们待在该死的田野中\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And we're in the middle of a fucking field.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎无可救药的战场\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A hopeless battle theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎除了这片土地‎什么都没有\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Except this whole land
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只有田野和森林\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}is nothing but fields and forests.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但他们还是投身战斗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But they did it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们永远停不下来 对吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We'd never stop, would we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎胜利的条件就是不停地战斗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Victory condition is just fighting and holding
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎维持她整个疯狂的帝国架构\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}the whole insane structure of her empire together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎直到我老死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}until I die of old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我希望我是错的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I want to be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我希望你是错的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I want you to be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎-我们能做到  -‎我们能做到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- We could do it. - We could.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们要永远这样做\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But we'd be doing it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你要永远在这里战斗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You'd be out here fighting forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我会回到施第里尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'd be back at Styria
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎永远努力保持供应线的顺畅\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}trying to keep supply lines intact forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们再也不会见面\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And we'd never see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎对不起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.99,0:22:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我希望我是错的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I want to be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.17,0:22:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们在白昼的冷光里 哼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're in the cold light of day, ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而卡米拉的宏大计划…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And Carmilla's grand plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎人类要为自己在世上的地位而战\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The humans are going to fight for their place in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎总是如此\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎在白昼的冷光里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}In the cold light of day,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.43,0:22:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我要问自己\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have to ask myself this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.97,0:22:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想这样吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do I want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果我们...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do we want this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可以一起做其他事 ‎我们还想这样吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}when we can do so much else together?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,‎姐妹们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎赫克托终于准备好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hector is finally ready
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:22:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎开始制造黑暗生物了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to start making night creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎回家吧 ‎要开始了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Come home. It begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎比我想象的还要糟糕\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's worse than I could have imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.94,0:23:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我这辈子见过不少破败的城镇\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I've seen more than a few wrecked towns in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不明白的是...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What I don't understand is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎德古拉先袭击这里 ‎因为他妻子死在这儿 对吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Dracula hit it first, when his wife died here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.13,0:23:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但这里到处是吸血鬼和黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But it's still infested with vampires and night creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:23:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们的最终目的是什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's their endgame here, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.92,0:24:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们能得到什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What do they get?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这些人根本没机会恢复和重建\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}These people never had a chance to recover and rebuild.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.40,0:24:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎太可怕了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一切都把我们引到这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And everything has led us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也就是说 我们来这里是有原因的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Which means we are here for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.08,0:24:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不知道我们怎么融入这座城市\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not sure how we fit into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.58,0:24:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎融入\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.46,0:24:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎嗯\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.58,0:24:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎等等\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.96,0:24:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是什么东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.58,0:24:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎可能不是我想的那样 但…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, it can't be what I think it is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.10,0:24:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你们来了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Ah, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.96,0:24:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好好看了我们漂亮的城市吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Getting a good look at our fine city?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.92,0:24:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我宁愿好好看看你的地下宫廷\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'd rather get a good look at your Underground Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.45,0:24:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还不行\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.21,0:24:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我想先确定可以相信你们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I want to be certain you can be trusted first.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.97,0:24:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎太好了 因为我们想先确定\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's good, because we want to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.00,0:24:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们可以相信你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}we can trust you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.54,0:25:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你忘了在跟谁说话\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You forget who you're speaking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.33,0:25:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们需要时间到处看看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We'd like some time to look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.46,0:25:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我相信你稍后能再找到我们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You can find us again later, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.99,0:25:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我们有重要的事情要讨论\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But we have important matters to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.64,0:25:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎拯救城市 恢复王位\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Saving the city. Restoring the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.33,0:25:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎发布命令\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Imposing order.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.69,0:25:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们也有很重要的事情要谈\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We have important matters to discuss too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.27,0:25:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎在此期间 我们要看看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}In the meantime, we're going to take a good long look
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.33,0:25:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你到现在都没能做到的事情\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}at how you've failed to do any of that so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.46,0:25:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎以及我们是否选择帮助你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And whether we're going to choose to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.77,0:25:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她确实需要我们的帮助\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She does need our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.95,0:25:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我厌倦了在别人的故事里客串\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But I am sick of being a bit player in someone else's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.83,0:25:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎走吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Walk away.
